    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "For sale is a dependable vehicle in good condition, ideal for a buyer who prioritizes mechanical health and a clean interior. The engine runs smoothly and has been regularly serviced, and the cabin remains comfortable and free of major wear. While the exterior paint still shines, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and some light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Overall, it is a solid, well-maintained car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
